# Privacy Policy for [Bot Name]

**Effective Date:** [Insert Date]

[Bot Name] is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect when you use the Bot, how we use it, and your rights regarding that data.

---

## Information We Collect

We collect only the information necessary to operate the Bot in your server:

- Discord server ID and channel ID(s) where the Bot operates  
- Discord user IDs of server members (to manage access/subscriptions)  
- Total number of members in the server  

**Note:** We do **not** store your messages, personal chats, or any other sensitive personal data. This is limited to basic identifiers and usage information.

---

## How We Use Your Information

Your data is used to:

- Operate and deliver the Bot’s features  
- Monitor usage and improve the Bot  
- Provide support to users  
- Manage subscriptions and billing  

We may also use aggregated, anonymized data for analytics and research to develop new features. We do **not** use your data for unrelated purposes.

---

## Sharing of Information

We do **not** sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information only:

- When required by law (e.g., subpoena or court order)  
- To protect our legal rights  

Otherwise, your data remains under our control.

---

## Data Retention

We retain your information only as long as necessary to provide the Bot’s services or as required by law. If your server is inactive for a prolonged period or you request deletion, we will remove your data.

---

## Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction, including secure servers and up-to-date security practices.  

**Important:** No system is perfectly secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.

---

## Your Rights

You may:

- Request access to your personal information  
- Request correction of any errors  
- Request deletion of your data  

To exercise these rights, contact us at [Your Email]. We will respond to valid requests as soon as reasonably possible.

---

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Updated versions will be posted on our Discord or website. Continued use of the Bot after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.

---

## Contact

For questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, contact us at:

[Your Email]

---

**Note for Server Owners:** Server owners are responsible for informing their members about this Privacy Policy.
